title: Carolina gives validity to 5-0 start winning in Seattle
text:
> North Carolina Carolina gives validity to 5-0 start winning in Seattle Carolina Panthers running back Jonathan Stewart (28) celebrates after scoring a touchdown against the Seattle Seahawks in the second half of an NFL football game as Panthers quarterback Cam Newton (1) looks on, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Seattle. (AP Photo/Elaine Thompson)
